short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AlgoArchive is a browser extension that automatically saves your LeetCode submissions to your GitHub account.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AlgoArchive is a Chrome extension that automatically grabs the leetcode or hackerrank problem and its solution from the web page and pushes it to github. The extension is designed to help users save and organize their submissions on GitHub, making it easier to track their progress and share their solutions with others.
